  <body>
    <section name="TypeBodyPadding">
      <p>Since Checkstyle 13.9.0</p>
      <subsection name="Description" id="TypeBodyPadding_Description">
        <div>
          Checks the padding of the body of type definitions (classes, interfaces,
          enums, records).
          That is, whether a blank line is required immediately after the opening brace
          and/or immediately before the closing brace of type bodies.
          Empty type bodies are exempt from this check by default.
        </div>

        <p>
          A blank line (padding) line is a line containing only whitespace characters.
        </p>

        <ul>
        <li>
          Property <code>starting</code> - Require a blank line after the type body opening
          brace.
          Type: <code>boolean</code>.
          Default value: <code>true</code>.
        </li>
        <li>
          Property <code>ending</code> - Require a blank line before the type body closing
          brace.
          Type: <code>boolean</code>.
          Default value: <code>true</code>.
        </li>
        <li>
          Property <code>allowEmpty</code> - Allow empty type bodies (no members) to omit
          the blank lines.
          Type: <code>boolean</code>.
          Default value: <code>true</code>.
        </li>
        <li>
          Property <code>skipInner</code> - Control whether to skip checking of inner types.
          Type: <code>boolean</code>.
          Default value: <code>true</code>.
        </li>
        <li>
          Property <code>skipLocal</code> - Control whether to skip checking of local types.
          Type: <code>boolean</code>.
          Default value: <code>true</code>.
        </li>
        <li>
          Property <code>tokens</code> - tokens to check
          Type: <code>java.lang.String[]</code>.
          Validation type: <code>tokenSet</code>.
          Default value:
          <a href=
          "https://checkstyle.org/apidocs/com/puppycrawl/tools/checkstyle/api/TokenTypes.html#CLASS_DEF">
          CLASS_DEF</a>,
          <a href=
          "https://checkstyle.org/apidocs/com/puppycrawl/tools/checkstyle/api/TokenTypes.html#INTERFACE_DEF">
          INTERFACE_DEF</a>,
          <a href=
          "https://checkstyle.org/apidocs/com/puppycrawl/tools/checkstyle/api/TokenTypes.html#ENUM_DEF">
          ENUM_DEF</a>,
          <a href=
          "https://checkstyle.org/apidocs/com/puppycrawl/tools/checkstyle/api/TokenTypes.html#RECORD_DEF">
          RECORD_DEF</a>,
          <a href=
          "https://checkstyle.org/apidocs/com/puppycrawl/tools/checkstyle/api/TokenTypes.html#ANNOTATION_DEF">
          ANNOTATION_DEF</a>.
        </li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          Parent is <code>com.puppycrawl.tools.checkstyle.TreeWalker</code>
        </p>

        <p>
          Violation Message Keys:
        </p>
        <ul>
        <li>
          <code>type.body.padding.after.lcurly</code>
        </li>
        <li>
          <code>type.body.padding.before.rcurly</code>
        </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>

